{"tid":1453783,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"任天堂新機 Switch Lite 拆解，發現電量從原版的16Wh減少到13.6Wh...","createTime":"2019-08-12T05:19:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T06:07:00.000Z","uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3739be78d7c1ed009587c7a3f2afb8ab85150ee4","tid":1453783,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:19:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.xfastest.com/nintendo/67907/nintendo-switch-lite-teardown/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.xfastest.com%2Fnintendo%2F67907%2Fnintendo-switch-lite-teardown%2F&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpAomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=2eb203aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.xfastest.com/nintendo/67907/nintendo-switch-lite-teardown/</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.xfastest.com/data/attachment/forum/201908/06/110632h5y5cry96v72vqy8.jpg.thumb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.xfastest.com%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F201908%2F06%2F110632h5y5cry96v72vqy8.jpg.thumb.jpg&h=3895ae55&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n任天堂在上個月突然發布了Switch Lite遊戲機，在取消了Joy-Con可拆卸手柄設計後，新機被定位在掌上游戲機市場，有著比原版Switch更好的電池續航能力，雖然Switch Lite還要到9月20日才正式開賣，但近日美國的監管機構FCC卻有任天堂這台新掌機的內部拆解圖給大家看了。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.xfastest.com/data/attachment/forum/201908/06/110626xuu3qbquqa73gqmk.jpg.thumb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.xfastest.com%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F201908%2F06%2F110626xuu3qbquqa73gqmk.jpg.thumb.jpg&h=52a913a2&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n因為Switch Lite在美上市需要經過FCC對網絡通訊部件的認證，所以國外網站 ffid . io (<a href=\"https://fccid.io/BKEHDH001/Internal-Photos/04-Short-Term-Confidential-Internal-Photo-4376240\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffccid.io%2FBKEHDH001%2FInternal-Photos%2F04-Short-Term-Confidential-Internal-Photo-4376240&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpAomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=594dc313\" target=\"_blank\">https://fccid.io/BKEHDH001/Internal-Photos/04-Short-Term-Confidential-Internal-Photo-4376240</a>) 挖掘到了任天堂新掌機的內部拆解檔案，得以了解新機的一些深入訊息，而從放出的拆解照片來看，Switch Lite內部依然有類似筆記型電腦所用的熱管 +風扇散熱系統，這部分下面為新機的新Soc，來自NVIDIA提供的定製版Tegra X1，據稱新SoC採用更先進的工藝製程，有更好功耗控制，也潛在更好一些的性能，但目前還沒有實機測試，所以這只是猜測。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.xfastest.com/data/attachment/forum/201908/06/110418rvmzf4wr7v2wnfvx.jpg.thumb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.xfastest.com%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F201908%2F06%2F110418rvmzf4wr7v2wnfvx.jpg.thumb.jpg&h=77da5bdd&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"1b7b37594ba4f9082132496a012f25688a1d9438","tid":1453783,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:19:48.000Z","msg":"至於在任天堂的標稱續航能力上，Switch Lite的電池比原版Switch多了一個小時，達到5-6個小時，但從拆解發現新機的電池容量其實變小了，從原版的16Wh減少到13.6Wh，續航反而有提升應該是因為新機的屏幕尺寸更小了，而手柄不能拆卸後，也不再需要為它充電，另外還有上面提到SoC的改進等在內多項變化所帶來的。<br />\n<br />\n不同於原版Switch的&ldquo;ODIN&rdquo;代號，Switch Lite的PCB主板上顯示它的代號&ldquo;VALI&rdquo;，這應該是代表&ldquo;Valkyrie&rdquo;，由此推測任天堂還會有個&ldquo;The Son of Odin&rdquo;，也就是漫威迷們熟悉的&ldquo;Thor&rdquo;，這可能會是傳聞中性能更強、定位更高的Switch Pro。"},{"pid":"dff0c8706a15243945e6ef5655bc0253aaa74026","tid":1453783,"uid":235152,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:09:20.000Z","msg":"賣垃圾"},{"pid":"a3d4b158a26a3d87e1643a25d8b7fa8f8e021b8a","tid":1453783,"uid":21378,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:02:59.000Z","msg":"弱化版. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3b7d74ed16bf472a5514ad8bdb0a89064e49747","tid":1453783,"uid":99209,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:01:20.000Z","msg":"將原來要叉電既整走，又慳返筆<br />\n老任呢招高呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aec2704bfa02d334e8842b5599f10bdf8d6d265","tid":1453783,"uid":12877,"like":8,"dislike":5,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:04:16.000Z","msg":"Switch = on9"},{"pid":"f0e717714bf3c99a6c801510ad6c3657e90c47b6","tid":1453783,"uid":115082,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:50:51.000Z","msg":"未公佈Switch果時又話唔會取代3DS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"638fa42055eb2f7567a58ad669255d7917d72610","tid":1453783,"uid":265449,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:55:30.000Z","msg":"仲好意思話出switch pro笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5781fc0a4c5b88e2a9406962eae1ae1ec24b30ab","tid":1453783,"uid":276297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:53:53.000Z","msg":"又開始行NDS條路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ee7113027c0080249e292b84a3b0f3f983acc90","tid":1453783,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:14:31.000Z","msg":"買部畀老母玩下都好"},{"pid":"e172b7adbc7ec079d5cd47686c5bd88abe8ba4c2","tid":1453783,"uid":1986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T16:55:21.000Z","msg":"咁買新版定舊版好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e43dd152b5d4c1442b9f758b9d5b0593e01c1bc8","tid":1453783,"uid":22288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:38:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"353bceb35864164adda2c912fd25e244b1763c06","tid":1453783,"uid":114839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e172b7adbc7ec079d5cd47686c5bd88abe8ba4c2","tid":1453783,"uid":1986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T16:55:21.000Z","msg":"咁買新版定舊版好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T10:21:37.000Z","msg":"依部係純手提版，電池細d但其實續航時間長左少少，便幾舊<br />\n另外重有部少改版既switch2019，電池容量同原版一樣，<br />\n但續航長左50%左右，同原版同價"},{"pid":"3ef5032450b6b3249a0df209c4e965a216ef5a70","tid":1453783,"uid":22288,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"cited